ates rules for products' seasonal availability with sales.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nGo to \"Sales -> Products -> Product seasonal config lines\"\nto create rules for your products.\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\n- Make rounding configurable\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues/new?body=module:%20sale_product_seasonality%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n\\# Damien Crier \\<<mailto:damien.crier@camptocamp.com>>\n\\* Simone Orsi \\<<mailto:simone.orsi@camptocamp.com>>\n\\* Julien Coux \\<<mailto:julien.coux@camptocamp.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/sale-workflow](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/14.0/sale_product_seasonality) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_product_seasonality.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_product_seasonality.models.sale_order", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_product_seasona